title: Looking for Plat V+ Duo partner.
body:
chicks chase elo
Current Rank: Plat IV 
add me. Im support main alistar naut great can morg and janna well.
got skype Cursevoice and teamspeak.

I am sick of going solo and being support having so many lanes being able to feed.
Looking for a duo partner who will win lane so that at least 3 members of the team (ADC,duo,me(supp)) can carry.
Aiming for Diamond.

replies.body: Yo im plat 4 atm i can potentially start duoing with you starting sunday? would be keen maining jung/riven/vayne myself
